‚Ä¢ The theoretical execution time of OMPCG is not well predicted for small problems, but for large problems
there is practically no inÔ¨Çuence of the parameters R(c) and M(c) in equation 4 and the prediction is satisfactory.
‚Ä¢ In OMPFG the cost of these parameters is higher, which is more apparent for small problems. For the largest
